Subject: [PATCH 3/3] cirrus: add blit_is_unsafe call to cirrus_bitblt_cputovideo

CIRRUS_BLTMODE_MEMSYSSRC blits do NOT check blit destination
and blit width, at all.  Oops.  Fix it.

