```
Description:
GNU paxutils is a suite of archive utilities: it will provide cpio, tar and POSIX pax archivers.

A fuzzing on tar and pax shows multiple crashes.
I really dont know if atm those tools are used somewhere.

Details:

# tar -t -f $FILE
